        <h1 class="text-center mb-5">About GoWrite</h1>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>GoWrite was born from a simple idea: everyone has a story worth telling. We believe in the power of words to connect, inspire, and transform lives. Our platform provides writers with the tools they need to share their voices with the world.</p>
                
                <h2 class="mt-4">Our Mission</h2>
                <p>To create a vibrant community where writers can grow, connect, and share their stories with readers worldwide. We're committed to making writing and publishing accessible to everyone.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
