                    <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1311078906/photo/portrait-of-handsome-young-man-wearing-sunglasses-and-white-tshirt-posing-on-city-street.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=VJnG1hCQ5TLLvRFyQpwzQd7kUFqgfmKaJ1g2E7oYmTA=" alt="Team Member">
